# Hoist pdfjs-dist into the top-level node_modules so Next.js/Webpack can
# resolve it. react-pdf pulls in pdfjs-dist as a peer; without this, pnpm's
# strict isolation puts it inside .pnpm/ where the Webpack chunk resolver
# mangles its .mjs module init (surfaces as "Object.defineProperty called
# on non-object" at runtime).
# Ref: https://github.com/wojtekmaj/react-pdf#configure-pdfjs-worker
public-hoist-pattern[]=*pdfjs-dist*
